{
  "texts": [
    "The P values for d, h and k are based on one-sided paired t-tests.",
    "f,g, AUC and AUPR ratio of cis-regulatory potential in naive CD4 + cells.",
    "The ground truth for f-h is promoter-capture Hi-C data.",
    "RE-TG pairs are divided into six distance groups ranging from 0-5 kb to 100-200 kb.",
    "PCC is calculated between the expression of TG and the chromatin accessibility of RE."
  ]
}